latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY ONE YEAR TO OUR BESTFRIENDSHIP, DUMMIE🤞🏻❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
6th September 2019 🤞🏻, the day I started to smile even more , the day I got the best person , the day I got my bestfriend , the day I met you , dumbass and here we are completing 
one year of happiness , one year of smiles with you , one year of love , one year of bestfriendship , one year and more to go.🥺❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my world in just one year ,😌❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my smile in just one year ,🥺❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my happiness in just one year ,😌❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my bestfriend in just one year ,🥺❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my strenght in just one year ,😌❤️
I can't thank you enough for becoming my support system in just one year ,🥺❤️
I can't thank you enough for doing so much for me in just one year ,😌❤️
One year is a really short period of time compared to how close we are right now. You made that place in my life in just one year which others couldn't make in so many years.You changed me in a positive way and made me as happy as I could ever be in just one year.😩❤️The risks we took , the memories we made , the times we laughed together , the times I cried on your shoulder , the times you got mad at me , the times we stood up for each
other , the times we fought , everything was so worth it. 🤭❤️I'm sorry for being annoying , I'm sorry for being so immature at times , but you have to bear me anyways , tho i'll improve myself and be a better person and make you feel proud. Thank you for tolerating me , caring about me , loving me , being there for me no matter what happens , and i promise to stay , I promise to be there for you and stand beside you no matter what happens. Ab thoda birthday ke liye bhi baaki rakhe? 🤭❤️
I love you way more than you do , way more than I've ever loved anyone else , way more than anyone else could ever imagine of loving you!🥰😚🤗😘🙁🥺🤭😌😩😭❤️👉🏼👈🏼
- babycakes🤞🏻❤️
